Then bring Más Agave Premium Hard Seltzer home to admire for yourself by heading to our beer finder at the link in our bio.

Our education team is saddened they can’t host all of you for their famous brewery tours. So, we decided to do the next best thing and start a weekly beer education video series. Starting today, we’ll be releasing weekly beer education videos to help you pass the time and hopefully, help you come out of this with some new beer knowledge.

In today’s video, John and Marklyn are talking about the importance of proper glassware. Grab a beer, pour it into your favorite mug, tumbler or snifter and let the beer education begin. If you enjoy this video feel free to let us know what other topics you would like them to cover in future videos. #chaseyourwhatif

node.text:
It’s time for another round of #CraftedinMI Collaboration Series beers – this time featuring @madcapcoffee of Grand Rapids and @leafmeco of Detroit!
 
First up we have Madcask Hazy IPA coming in at 6.6% ABV. Heavily inspired by the popular Painkiller cocktail, the addition of cascara (the dried fruit of the coffee cherry), orange, pineapple and coconut with citrusy and tropical hops will have you setting sail for your secret island hideaway. 
 
Next is Align Me Gruit Style Ale, which incorporates a bouquet of botanicals and herbs to represent each of the seven Chakras. Supported by spicy ginger and hibiscus flowers, this beer clocks in at 5.8% ABV and is a rare gem you won’t want to miss.
 
Both beers are extremely limited and will be available exclusively in our taprooms in 750mL bottles and on draft. Madcask Hazy IPA will release on September 24 and Align Me Gruit Style Ale will release on September 17. Both of our partners will be in their respective taprooms on release day, so head to the link in our bio for more info! #foundersbrewing
